1720
02:13:42,028 --> 02:13:55,820
We do not allow them, you know, part of the expectation, and this has been communicated in a few different areas, and it's continuous, this communication, is that students, if they have to make a phone call, they go to an office, we'll happily allow them to use the phone.

1721
02:13:56,200 --> 02:14:02,084
Also, they are not allowed to use headphones or listen to music during their hallway time either.

1722
02:14:02,404 --> 02:14:06,426
So it's not as if students have their headphones on or music is playing from their phones.

1723
02:14:06,746 --> 02:14:08,527
And this is part of the compromise we had with them.

1724
02:14:08,547 --> 02:14:12,830
We literally just had a discussion and treat them like adults and say, there are expectations we have.

1725
02:14:13,190 --> 02:14:17,433
And there are reasons for those expectations, for safety and for like reasons.

1726
