Well, and that's exactly what I'm saying, that if parents start reading this, they're going to jump to conclusions.

2338
03:07:31,881 --> 03:07:34,402
And I don't want parents to have the fear out there.

2339
03:07:34,762 --> 03:07:39,325
And I don't want the students to have the fear out there, no matter which group or subgroup they're in.

2340
03:07:39,785 --> 03:07:43,547
And that's why I said it's very important that we do discuss this the proper way.

2341
03:07:43,767 --> 03:07:46,309
And not starting rumors out there.

2342
03:07:46,529 --> 03:07:48,210
I think that's incredibly important.

2343
03:07:48,350 --> 03:07:53,172
I think unfortunately some of the information presented here tonight is the victim of that.

2344
03:07:53,573 --> 03:07:58,736
There are some confused narratives that I think would be better served if we could clarify.

2345
03:07:58,756 --> 03:08:01,037
But specifically to GPA and school grades.

2346
03:08:01,657 --> 03:08:11,268
