2347
03:08:11,949 --> 03:08:18,576
We have to invest substantially in those systems, in our own internal systems, if we're going to keep up with the expectations of the state.

2348
03:08:19,316 --> 03:08:21,517
This is all new territory for us, obviously.

2349
03:08:21,877 --> 03:08:23,117
It changes on a yearly basis.

2350
03:08:23,538 --> 03:08:26,899
But it should be a priority of the school committee and of the school system itself.

2351
03:08:27,519 --> 03:08:34,621
The data systems that we presently have and how to increase in support and actually add to those systems.

2352
03:08:36,182 --> 03:08:36,582
Thank you.

2353
03:08:37,122 --> 03:08:37,402
Mayor?

2354
03:08:38,202 --> 03:08:38,882
Mr. Skerry.

2355
03:08:39,123 --> 03:08:43,344
